<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
A <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> columnar <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft with moulding at top and bottom (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre" precision="circa">1.12</measure>, diam. <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre" precision="circa">0.48</measure>); there is a channel (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.095</measure>) down one side from just below the upper moulding to the bottom, and a clamp hole cut in the lower moulding approximately opposite it.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on two sides with almost identical texts each within a raised <rs type="decoration">tabella ansata</rs>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02-0.022</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>

<p>
<date notAfter="0100" notBefore="0001" exact="none" cert="low">First century A.D.</date>
 possibly Julio-Claudian (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
